{"tid":664677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際評級機構　標準普爾　因中港融合加深　降香港長期信用評級","createTime":"2018-05-14T09:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T13:51:28.000Z","uid":47714,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fb56ef71d4e6c27e2a3f23c0e1e7e224c4647fee","tid":664677,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1506045478684&amp;issue=20170922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1506045478684%26issue%3D20170922&d=jP1xHi%2F8I8lBzWYhOTrsJ8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=6b820f6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1506045478684&amp;issue=20170922</a><br />\n<br />\n評級機構標準普爾繼昨日下調中國長期主權評級後，今日再降香港長期信貸評級，由「AAA」下調至「AA+」，以反映潛在的溢出風險，展望由「負面」調至「穩定」。<br />\n<br />\n標普另確認香港短期信貸評級為「A-1+」。<br />\n<br />\n標普指，有見中港兩地制度上及政策上有強烈聯繫，而中國去槓桿化帶來的破壞力，較該行預期的嚴重，故繼降中國評級後，亦下調香港評級，以反映潛在的溢出風險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E5%8F%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8B%96%E7%B4%AF-%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE%E9%99%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E6%81%86%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E8%B7%8C%E9%80%BE200%E9%BB%9E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E5%258F%2597%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258B%2596%25E7%25B4%25AF-%25E6%25A8%2599%25E6%2599%25AE%25E9%2599%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%25A9%2595%25E7%25B4%259A-%25E6%2581%2586%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25B7%258C%25E9%2580%25BE200%25E9%25BB%259E%2F&d=jP1xHi%2F8I8lBzWYhOTrsJ8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=bd11e887\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E5%258F%2597%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258B%2596%25E7%25B4%25AF-%25E6%25A8%2599%25E6%2599%25AE%25E9%2599%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%25A9%2595%25E7%25B4%259A-%25E6%2581%2586%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25B7%258C%25E9%2580%25BE200%25E9%25BB%259E%2F&h=6762e565\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E5%8F%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8B%96%E7%B4%AF-%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE%E9%99%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E6%81%86%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E8%B7%8C%E9%80%BE200%E9%BB%9E/</a><br />\n<br />\n評級機構標準普爾繼昨日將中國主權信用評級下調一級，由原先的「AA-」下降至「A+」後，再將香港主權信用評級由「AAA」下降至「AA+」，並將展望由「負面」調整至「穩定」。"},{"pid":"db7fea20e5351b3707bcb731c811058e52c6e346","tid":664677,"uid":20449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:44:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b18bccb6a95b4ecf28ac2927d40235e0325e51f","tid":664677,"uid":15135,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:51:48.000Z","msg":"開心啦，一體化，恨到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c484992707ad8246024a85ebd0ba72ab9993dbac","tid":664677,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:53:27.000Z","msg":"其實標普 穆迪個評級公信力係點黎"},{"pid":"784f12db5fc80c24d4541eaa162d95e18eac8ca0","tid":664677,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:55:47.000Z","msg":"要降到咩評級先影響到班基金佬對港投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56aacd31806a675b689cd747a07704cc9bd04a02","tid":664677,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089bc3fa0edefe5bf4efcd5a5c8acb74b3555ddf","tid":664677,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"784f12db5fc80c24d4541eaa162d95e18eac8ca0","tid":664677,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:55:47.000Z","msg":"要降到咩評級先影響到班基金佬對港投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi